# Privacy-oriented context exclusions for Codex CLI / future agents.
# The scripts are safe to inspect; captured source data and generated reports
# should only be read when a task explicitly needs them.

raw/**
parsed/**
reports/**
state/**

.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.token
*.secret
*.codex_output.md

.git/**
.DS_Store
__pycache__/**
